{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">|||||||||| Developer's Note ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I've always learned to make games by making games, and love making small, solid arcade games with simple mechanics. <strong>Expect 'X-teroids' to be a small, replayable arcade high-scoring game whose sole goal is to survive the game for 10 minutes while accumulating scores and unlocking a few extra skins.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>I appreciate the feedback and will do everything I can to ensure support for my game. If you experience problems with the game, please leave a review on the store page, or if you just want to say hello, please contact me via email.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Thank you for taking the time to read this article; I really hope you enjoy playing my game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>liangxie - Team SunnyTech</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">|||||||||| GAMEPLAY ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;X-teroids&quot; improves upon the original &quot;Asteroids&quot; game by adding features tailored to modern players. With just a mouse or joystick directional buttons, players can freely control their spaceship, but of course, skillful operation requires practice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">|||||||||| Feature ||||||||||</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition, several unique props can constitute emergent experiences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/\u5b50\u5f39x3\u7ed3\u5408\u73af\u5f62\u5b50\u5f39.gif?t=1738548373\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342540/extras/\u5b50\u5f39\u4f24\u5bb3\u548c\u73af\u7ed5\u5b50\u5f39.gif?t=1738548373\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img cl